## ğŸ“ Dataset Information

The dataset contains 2290 rows and 6 columns:

- `Date`: Timestamp (not used in modeling)
- `SPX`: S&P 500 Index
- `GLD`: Gold Price (Target)
- `USO`: Crude Oil ETF Price
- `SLV`: Silver ETF Price
- `EUR/USD`: Forex Rate

